name: Sha Doo Be Doop
description:
Miss Nina's 2013 release features and eclectic mix of music for children ages 1 to 6. You'll find everything from child appropriate rap & hip-hop to songs inspired by Miss Nina's favorite children's books.

Track List:
1.  My Hula Hoop
2.  How Do Dinosaurs Say Goodnight
3.  Angry Song
4.  New Alphabet
5.  Ba-Rump
6.  The Brown Bear Rap
7.  Sing Your Way Home
8.  Ridin' In My Car
9.  Wild Things
10. Wash Our Hands
11. Grateful
12. Bye-Bye, Everybody

name: Singing & Dancing Together
description:
Miss Nina's 2009 CD debut won a Parents' Choice Recommended Award.  A mix of Miss Nina originals & traditional children's music featuring "Hello Hello", "Three Little Fishies" and the musical rendition of the book "This Jazz Man."

Track List:
1.  Hello Hello
2.  Three Little Fishies
3.  Chugga Chugga
4.  Sing-Along Medley
5.  This Jazz Man
6.  Beanstalk Blues
7.  Opposite Day
8.  Spinning Statues
9.  Zig Zug
10. Me and My Teddy Bear
11. Singing & Dancing Together
